name: kerbalism-chemicalplant
title: Chemical Plant
description: This versatile chemical plant will give you basic ISRU and recycling capabilities.

name: kerbalism-fuelcell
title: Fuel Cell
description: A 1kW fuel cell. Will generate 10.248 l of water per day, using 11.64 units of H2 and 23.04 units of O2. These figures were determined by theoretical calculations and don't include boil-off. Better technology will unlock lighter configurations.

name: kerbalism-lifesupportmodule
title: External ECLSS Module
description: This external life support module will allow you to add processors to your crewed spacecrafts. Any additional process that you'll unlock with future nodes will become available in the Configure Module.
